  "text": "[TO BE PUBLISHED IN THE GAZETTE OF INDIA, EXTRAORDINARY, PART II, SECTION 3, SUB-SECTION (i)] GOVERNMENT OF INDIA MINISTRY OF FINANCE (DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE) Notification No. 13/2014 - Central Excise (N.T.) New Delhi, the 21 st March, 2014 30, Phalguna, Saka, 1935 G.S.R. (E).- In pursuance of rule 12CCC of the Central Excise Rules, 2002, and rule 12AAA of the CENVAT Credit Rules, 2004, the Central Board of Excise and Customs hereby rescinds the notification No. 6/2012- Central Excise (N.T.) dated the 13 th March, 2012 published in the Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, Section 3, Sub-section (i) vide number G.S.R. 142 (E) dated the 13 th March, 2012, except as respects things done or omitted to be done before such rescission. F. No. 267/13/2013-CX.8 (Pankaj Jain) Under Secretary to the Government of India -- 1 of 1 --",
